meta.description: There are things you can do as your pet's primary advocate to ensure your dog's or cat's risk of adverse vaccine reactions is minimal.

title: What Is Vaccinosis?
cleaned_text: Establishing protective immunity in pets through vaccination is important for preventing infectious diseases, but many pet parents don’t realize that more vaccines do not deliver more or better immunity
